PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Communiations of Kenneth C. Lee, of Edmonton, Alberta, as a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the National Museum of Science and Technology, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, effective June 21, 1993, in the place of Diane Chabot, whose term will expire.
